{"type": "article", "id": 7567, "title": "好莱坞 TOP 25 的造型师和他们的代表作", "description": "给好莱坞明星当造型师，这工作听起来足够让人心动了。", "date": "2015-03-19T15:46:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7240, "name": "造型师"}], "category": 19, "column": null, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 99, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160608131006ECSdXajpLrT60JWn.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t给好莱坞明星当造型师，<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">可以每天和美衣、配饰打交道，没事还能参加个好莱坞名流聚会什么的，</span>这工作听起来足够让人心动了。最近 <a href=\"http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/style/top-25-stylists-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">H<span>ollywoodreporter </span></a>列出了一个好莱坞 <span>TOP 25 的</span>造型师清单，看看她们的个人履历，也是能挖掘出不少励志故事呢。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong>PETRA FLANNERY</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130948neqIMEbzHpJ5g6dX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t“我极尽全力凸显客户的个性，我钟情于塑造特别时尚的形象。”<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><a href=\"http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/style/top-25-stylists-2015/petra-flannery/\" target=\"_blank\">Petra Flannery</a> </span>是个红毯上的冒险家。这个出生于旧金山的设计师在大学期间学的政治学，以前还做过模特代理。她是艾玛·斯通（<span>Emma Stone</span>）的御用造型师，他们是从 <span>House Bunny </span>时期开始合作的。斯通说，“我们都是热衷于冒险的女性。”<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130949TdUEaONQzyVjm6fD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>最佳作品：</em><span><em>Emma Stone </em></span><em>在金球奖上的装扮</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong>LESLIE FREMAR</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t如果要颁发一个“持续优雅奖”，那么非 <a href=\"http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/style/top-25-stylists-2015/leslie-fremar/\" target=\"_blank\">Leslie Fremar </a>莫属。她为奥斯卡奖获得者 <span>Julianne\r\nMoore </span>设计的礼服优雅动人。 <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130949HoBQL0vWZEk9fVzU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130949Ve9s3CnFr8iGpMjl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>最佳作品：</em><span><em>Julianne Moore </em></span><em>在金球奖颁奖礼上纪梵希裙装</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong>KARLA WELCH &amp; KEMAL HARRIS</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130950ShqC2cYLJZdktvNi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.51875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t“我们不追随潮流，而是想创造时尚的经典。”<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><a href=\"http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/style/top-25-stylists-2015/kemal-harris-karla-welch/\" target=\"_blank\">Harris </a></span>是《纸牌屋》第三季中 <span>Claire\r\nUnderwood </span>的服装设计师，没错，她通过服饰，将这个女人的形象精准的表现了出来。最近她刚开了一个 <span>Instagram </span>账号，经常发自己新作的照片。如果你对帅女人装感兴趣，不妨随时去 <span>catch </span>一下她的新动态。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130950t1D0OgmLe9fCWE2y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>最佳作品 ：Robin Wright 的一身西装</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong>KATE YOUNG</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606081309517gFVuCOakWoPYI0d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t《五十度灰》的女主角 Dakota Johnson 就是 <a href=\"http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/style/top-25-stylists-2015/kate-young/\" target=\"_blank\">KATE YOUNG</a> 的客户。娜塔莉·波特曼 Miss Dior 广告片里的造型也是她设计的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130951ubrtzSnWioNAqvCx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><em>最佳作品 </em></span><em>：</em><span><em>Dakota </em></span><em>在奥斯卡颁奖礼上的着装，这身打扮被 </em><span><em>Vogue 杂志</em></span><em>评为了“奥斯卡最佳着装”。</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong>ILARIA URBINATI</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130952mO2KxBvToi7leJ18.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t《性爱大师》被提名艾美奖，<span>Lizzy Caplan </span><a href=\"http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/emmy-awards-2014-lizzy-caplan-727927\" target=\"_blank\">一席黑色长裙</a>也亮瞎了红毯，这便是 <span>ILARIA\r\nURBINATI </span>的作品。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130953BmotjgDJSunw1i2Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\"><em>Lizzy Caplan</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130953a9YiMwfoJDPdRbGu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>最佳作品： </em><em>2015 </em><em>奥斯卡奖上 </em><em>Laura\r\nDern 的长裙。</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong>ELIZABETH STEWART</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130954UeJimYndRbZBvMxA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>ELIZABETH </span>是 <span>Blanchett </span>和 <span>Julia Roberts </span>的造型师。电影《蓝色茉莉》中 <span>Cate\r\nBlanchett 的造型便出自她手。</span> <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130954F0SCwMYs3uIhnHoU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>最佳着装：</em><span><em>Julia Roberts </em></span><em>在艾美奖上的裙装。</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong>LEITH CLARK</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130954NzJM0qxkFZ1jE39Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>在着装方面，Kiera\r\nKnightley 一向对取悦大众不感兴趣。从 2007 年开始，她开始与伦敦造型师 LEITH CLARK 合作，Clark 说，“我们在一起合作很长时间了，只创造那些我们认为对的衣服。”</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130955kxtT4zdpNsDUg3J8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>这就是 Clark 的作品。</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong>CRISTINA EHRLICH</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606081309558f1N7ecVRzW6XCZt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>Ehrlich </span>特别擅长为新明星打造造型。有不少明星都受益于她的设计和审美：<span>Allison Williams、Robbie 、</span><span>Gugu\r\nMbatha- Raw </span>和 <span>Uzo Aduba .</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130956oXR3DwJaxUbv0GzY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>最佳作品：Allison Williams 在艾美奖上穿着 </em><span style=\"white-space:normal;\"><em>Ehrlich 设计的晚礼服。</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong>JEANANN WILLIAMS</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130956NKwpahvzV6QgqY5i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.73125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t对明星来说，选对造型师简直太重要了，<span>WILLIAMS </span>的设计就让 <span><a href=\"http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/gallery/jeanann-williams-naomi-watts-gallery-782074\">Naomi Watts</a> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t成为了每年奥斯卡红毯上的亮点。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130957CcgldpPzvft3QEL8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>最佳作品：</em><span><em>2015 </em></span><em>奥斯卡奖上的 </em><span><em>Naomi Watts</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong>JOSEPH CASSELL</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130957IUXM2WRrnHFwv8kO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t1989 是她的专辑名也是出生年，但 2015 却是她在时尚圈站稳脚跟的年份。Taylor Swift 和 Cassell 已经在一起合作很长时间了，<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">她穿着 </span><span style=\"white-space:normal;\">Prada </span><span style=\"white-space:normal;\">的衣服出演了</span>“Blank Space”音乐录影带，这支 MV 已被累积播放了 6 亿次。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130958MlPc8Jb7nWIkY5EL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>最佳作品：</em><span style=\"white-space:normal;\"><em>Taylor Swift 身穿他设计的晚礼裙。</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">以上是 TOP 10 的的造型师，还有以下 15 位造型师值得介绍：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130958dHGF3L5h2f7lNmEr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>JESSICA PASTER </span>为 <span>Emily Blunt </span>打造的妆容<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130959TSqy2mxI8sPgajJB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>BRANDON MAXWEL </span>为 <span>Lady Gaga </span>设计的造型<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130959FkDoIMh7QAEm4RvP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\tRACHEL ZOE / RACHEL ZOE STUDIO 为 Jennifer\r\nLawrence 设计的迪奥礼服\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131000yj1mrbuBk8hP9WRe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>ERIN WALSH </span>为 <span>Sarah Jessica Parker </span>设计的礼服<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606081310003nXHbxRs7jY4MSzc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>MICAELA ERLANGER </span>为 <span>Lupita\r\nNyong'o </span>设计的 <span>CK </span>礼服<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131000eZoJ45FBhE7VgsHv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>JEANNE YANG </span>为 <span>Robert Downey </span>设计的服装<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/201606081310011Zjn37SvW0oDq2G9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\tROB ZANGARDI &amp; MARIEL HAENN 为 Jennifer Lopez\r\n所做的设计\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131001F4OUacPlo5fMnvw3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>RYAN HASTINGS </span>为 <span>Rosamund pike </span>设计的服装<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131002hESl2kHKZzsn3U8V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>SAMANTHA MCMILLEN </span>为 <span>Dakota Fanning </span>所做的设计<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131002d5AtE3rwI648vnks.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<p>\r\n\tJASON REMBERT 为 Rita Ora 设计的透视装\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131003Ry0uXhwzWoCO7iJ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>TARA SWENNEN </span>为 <span>Emily Ratajkowski </span>设计的晚礼服<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131003vHhkO98mPt4IX1E2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>REBECCA CORBIN-MURRAY </span>为 <span>James </span>设计的礼服<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131004CqOGAuWmiw86D3n4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>PENNY LOVELL </span>为 <span>Taylor Schilling （左）</span>设计的服装。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131005LCzIrwJGmZ4H60jK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>WENDI &amp; NICOLE FERREIRA </span>为 <span>Elizabeth Banks </span>设计的服装<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131005Z4Fx78JzpdrSObRc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>SOPHIE LOPEZ </span>为 <span>Kate Hudson</span>（左一）设计的礼服\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t如果想看更全的造型师照片，可以点击<a href=\"http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/style/top-25-stylists-2015/rebecca-corbin-murray/\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>。\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}